{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5c01a943cf","title":"复民盟马来亚露分部电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"16c325c944","index":0,"year":1946,"month":10,"day":8,"articleId":"5c01a943cf"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0000d0c921","type":"paragraph","text":"复民盟马来亚露分部电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"5c01a943cf"},{"id":"55a6e2dd77","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年10月8日）中国民主同盟马来亚露质分部盟员大会主席王廷俊先生钧鉴：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"5c01a943cf"},{"id":"4af0524779","type":"paragraph","text":"九月二十日代电敬悉，贵盟痛恶内战，呼呼和平，所提甚为切中时整，敬党自日寇投降之后，即以和平民主与独立为奋斗之自标，但国民党好战分子持有美政府外援，坚持独裁，坚持内战，破环政协决议、整军方案与停战协定。数月以来，以无理要求作为商谈条件，以推蔽其进行扩大内战之烟幕，发展至目前，已到最严重阶段。解决的关键为使一月政协决议切实付诸实施，希海外侨胞诸贤达，再接再历，为祖国之和平民主独立而努力，数党亦当本此方针奋斗到底。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"5c01a943cf"},{"id":"e5d422e060","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党中央委员会主席毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"5c01a943cf"},{"id":"a55925598f","type":"paragraph","text":"十月八日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"5c01a943cf"}],"page":{"id":"c9e796f053","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"5c01a943cf","start":214,"end":214}}}},"__N_SSG":true}